_sText: Aim_Shootout This map I made features weapons such as Dual Elites, Mac-10 and M3. The inicial weapons are the Dual Elites, while the other can be found in certain areas. It also has two grenades. It will also make it easier to do the Akimbo King achievement(Use Dual Elites to kill an enemy player who also has Dual Elites equipped). I hope you like the map. Please rate and assess your thoughts or any suggestions on how to improve on this. Map by 3nD Of the Lin3
